{"tid":895252,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"到底啲人係咪唔識排隊塔扶手電梯","createTime":"2018-11-09T04:50:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-22T03:40:33.000Z","uid":200366,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"edf8a179d8d2fe0503cf8f2dc1670f8b721ba576","tid":895252,"uid":200366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T04:50:17.000Z","msg":"繁忙時間 啲撚樣都係唔理後面排住幾多人<br />\n見有位就係側邊竊入黎 有冇諗過後面排緊隊既人感受 同打尖有咩分別<br />\n<br />\n非繁忙時間<br />\n總會有人貪快排左邊先 因為左邊多數都少人啲<br />\n跟住臨上電梯竊去右邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有係香港人都知左邊係比人行架啦<br />\n成日有D廢老、情侶、大陸哩好中意企係左邊阻撚住晒<br />\n要人出聲屌尻你先讓<br />\n除非你有特別原因我唔怪你<br />\n<br />\n再有邊個唔識排隊要插隊 我一定閘撚住你再撞開你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae86113bfe853f287e848a60f5f35b5fc3cab72f","tid":895252,"uid":200366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T06:21:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ac940b22348dd2c69bc040c6fda8f13f5f9189c3","tid":895252,"uid":9298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T06:23:36.000Z","msg":"岩岩落黎香港？"},{"pid":"6555b9fde5fb71e9aed036f4ca6320fee155bb59","tid":895252,"uid":206037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T06:30:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 鍵盤戰士"},{"pid":"3f97d7ea34185dbbbde6fd3a02fea92c7b7e3315","tid":895252,"uid":200366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac940b22348dd2c69bc040c6fda8f13f5f9189c3","tid":895252,"uid":9298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T06:23:36.000Z","msg":"岩岩落黎香港？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T03:40:33.000Z","msg":"想屌好耐 而家先講啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}